Package org.cpnsim.datacenter

Interface Datacenter

All Superinterfaces:
Comparable<SimEntity>, DatacenterPrice, Identifiable, Nameable, Runnable, SimEntity
All Known Implementing Classes:
DatacenterNull, DatacenterSimple
public interface Datacenter extends SimEntity, DatacenterPrice
An interface to be implemented by each class that represents a datacenter. It extends SimEntity and DatacenterPrice. The mainly components of a datacenter are the InterScheduler, LoadBalance, IntraScheduler, ConflictHandler, and StatesManager.
Since:
LGDCloudSim 1.0
Author:
Jiawen Liu
